类 BaseParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jmeter.protocol.http.parser.BaseParser

    public abstract class BaseParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements LinkExtractorParser
    BaseParser is the base class for LinkExtractorParser It is advised to make subclasses reusable across parsing, so BaseParserisReusable() returns true by default
    从以下版本开始:
    3.0

    • 方法详细资料

      • getParser

        public static LinkExtractorParser getParser(java.lang.String parserClassName)
                                     throws LinkExtractorParseException
        Factory method of parsers. Instances might get cached, when LinkExtractorParser.isReusable() on the newly created instance equals true.
        参数:
        parserClassName - name of the class that should be used to create new parsers
        返回:
        a possibly cached instance of the wanted LinkExtractorParser
        抛出:
        LinkExtractorParseException - when a new instance could not be instantiated

      • isReusable

        public boolean isReusable()
        Parsers should over-ride this method if the parser class is re-usable, in which case the class will be cached for the next getParser() call.
        指定者:
        isReusable 在接口中 LinkExtractorParser
        返回:
        true if the Parser is reusable
